[B][COLOR="Orange"][SIZE="3"]DESCRIPTION[/SIZE][/COLOR][/B]

This add-on is a Masque Skin. You have to install [URL="https://www.wowinterface.com/downloads/info12097"]Masque[/URL] first in order to use it.
This skin is pretty simple and clean. It comes with a 1 Pixel border, no shadows and a plain or World of Warcraft backdrop.


[B][COLOR="Orange"][SIZE="3"]INSTALLATION[/SIZE][/COLOR][/B]

Download the file and extract the package in your World of Warcraft add-on directory.

Retail: "World of Warcraft\_retail_\Interface\AddOns"
Classic: "World of Warcraft\_classic_\Interface\AddOns"


[B][COLOR="Orange"][SIZE="3"]BUGS & FEATURES[/SIZE][/COLOR][/B]

Please, don't be shy and contact me if you found a bug. I'll try to fix it as fast as possible.


[SIZE="1"][COLOR="DimGray"]Last Update: 08/13/2019[/COLOR][/SIZE]
